  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Receptionist",
  "description": "<p>Gross: $2000 - $2300</p><p>5 day work week (rotating shift)</p><p>Working hours (8-hr shift):</p><ul><li>7.15am to 3.15pm or 1pm to 9pm on weekdays</li><li>7.30am to 3.30pm or 8am to 4pm on weekend/PH</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><u>Responsibilities</u></p><ul><li>Welcoming members & assisting with check-ins</li><li>Building rapport with new and existing members</li><li>Handling payments when required</li><li>Assisting with bookings, cancellations or requests by members</li><li>Achieving membership monthly target set by HQ</li><li>Attending to phone/walk-in/email/text enquiries</li><li>Actively seeking new sale opportunities</li><li>Maintaining studio's cleanliness</li><li>Printing and emailing EOD sales reports to Directors</li><li>All other ad-hoc duties given by Store Manager</li></ul><p><u>Requirements</u></p><ul><li>Pleasant personality and loves meeting new people</li><li>Relevant working experience in customer service and/or sales</li><li>Outstanding communication skills</li><li>Basic computer skills</li><li>A great team player with strong initiative</li><li>Ability to multitask</li><li>Reliable and punctual</li><li>Fluency in English oral and written. </li><li>Having a fitness background will be an added advantage!</li></ul>",
